  "detailed_description": "Dare to be scared!  After 30 years, Atari's classic groundbreaking game is back - with all-new scream-worthy chills and thrills!  With spooky enemies lurking around every corner, are you brave enough to enter the Haunted House?<br>\t\t\t\t\t   <strong>KEY FEATURES:</strong><br>\t\t\t\t\t   <ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Explore the dark depths of Graves Mansion - find your way through 20 dark and eerie levels - just don't let the ghosts send you running scared!                                  <br>\t\t\t\t\t\t     </li><li>Uncover dark secrets - solve the mystery of what happened to your long-lost grandfather!<br>\t\t\t\t\t   </li></ul>",
